WebScrapeToFile - Class in application
A Class that will scrape text from given URI and write to a file.
WebScrapeToFile() - Constructor for class application.WebScrapeToFile
 
Word - Class in application
Word Class objects are created from HashMap (key=word, value=frequency) and implements Comparable so ArrayList can be sorted and overrides toString() to print results to console.
Word(String, int) - Constructor for class application.Word
 
WordFrequencyAnalyzer - Class in application
A Class which instantiates a Word object with each entry of HashMap (K/V = word/frequency) and adds to an ArrayList to enable sorting and printing (Word implements Comparable).
WordFrequencyAnalyzer() - Constructor for class application.WordFrequencyAnalyzer
